esielt vanlig tematikk i en humoristisk barnebok. Veier du ordene dine n\u00f8ye?", "-  Nei, nei det g\u00e5r ikke. N\u00e5r f\u00f8rst dette er tema m\u00e5 en g\u00e5 \u00aball in\u00bb. Jeg tenker ikke p\u00e5 hvem jeg skriver for mens jeg skriver. Da bare koser jeg meg, gliser Erlend Loe, som legger til at han tror denne m\u00e5ten \u00e5 behandle tematikken kan v\u00e6re befriende for barna ogs\u00e5."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "1c0029ace3f1a3e8ae255b71bfedcc6beac793508d47f1bc547610c6fd10c69f"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-29T22:34:01.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Publikum p\u00e5 den litter\u00e6re hagefesten i Adrianstua s\u00f8ndag ble be\u00e6ret med en verdenspremiere. Erlend Loe leste hele f\u00f8rste kapittel p\u00e5 den neste boka om truckf\u00f8rer Kurt."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/kultur/article11486617.ece/dljksh/ALTERNATES/w980-default/AdrianstuaHOVED.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/56f5cd0486d916efdc76351ac7d552dafbbd2924.jpg?59249ec9"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Hektet p\u00e5 dommedag -adressa.no", "Voksenroman om to uker", "M\u00e5 g\u00e5 \u00aball in\u00bb"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "56f5cd0486d916efdc76351ac7d552dafbbd2924"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Erlend loe"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Erlend loe"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "kultur"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["all in", "loe", "litter\u00e6r hagefest"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["loes", "national geographic channels", "adrianstua", "slutten", "doomsday preppers", "adresseavisen", "kurt"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "val